data.description: Welcome HOME y'all to this 5 bedroom 3 FULL bath in the brand NEW, highly sought after SECKINGER High School district. SO many incredible features but what really sets this home apart is its commitment to energy efficiency with SOLAR PANELS that provide green home, renewable energy. You can have peace of mind knowing that your carbon footprint is being reduced & your MONTHLY utility savings is INCREDIBLE. The open spacious floor plan here is perfect for a growing family & boasts brand NEW luxury vinyl plank wood flooring throughout the entire home!! Vaulted ceilings in your family room & a separate dining room that also opens to the living area is perfect for Holiday gatherings. Your kitchen features NEW stainless steel appliances, gorgeous granite counters, breakfast bar & beautiful cabinetry + an eat in kitchen space. Just off the family room you will find the primary and secondary bedrooms on the main upper floor. Your oversized primary suite features a sitting room; perfect for coffee in the morings, even a small nursery or office space. Primary also features an en-suite spa bathroom with separate soaking tub & step in shower PLUS walk in closet. Secondary bedrooms are spacious and share the full hall bath. Downstairs you will find a walk out terrace level entertaining space with a HUGE recreation room, home gym, or second living room PLUS an oversized 4th bedroom complete with recording studio/closet with sound proof paneling. You will also find the 5th bedroom and en-suite full bathroom, perfect for a private guest suite or even home office. Community boasts a pool, tennis AND playground- Low HOA and NO rental restrictions either. LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION: Located in the HEART of Buford, literally minutes to BOTH 85 hwy & 985 making commuting simple. Just a few minutes to the Mall of Georgia, community concerts & events, golf courses, top notch dining, area parks, green belts & SO much MORE.
